response.overview: Novelist Catherine Tramell is once again in trouble with the law, and Scotland Yard appoints psychiatrist Dr. Michael Glass to evaluate her. Though, like Detective Nick Curran before him, Glass is entranced by Tramell and lured into a seductive game.
response.tagline: Everything interesting begins in the mind
response.title: Basic Instinct 2

titles.title: Basic Instinct 2 - Neues Spiel für Catherine Tramell
